    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 operating points in validation testing. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Overall credibility assessment supports regulatory submission.",
